</entry><entry thead="no"><para>glyph placement layout    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>LayoutPlaceholder()</computeroutput>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>LayoutEngine</computeroutput> public static internal API   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>header exposed   </para>
